    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Keep small objects safe and organized with the 100pk 3&quot; x 3&quot; Plastic Bag Set! The 100pk of 3&quot; x 3&quot; Plastic Bags is a great addition to any home, office, garage or workshop. Each set comes with 100 individual clear plastic bags. Each bag is self locking with a single zipper, so they can be used over and over again. These bags are 2mm thick, and measure in at just 3&quot; x 3&quot;, the perfect size for organizing vitamins, medicine, small jewelry and other tiny items while not in use. Make sure to keep a pack of these around for household use, storage and organization while traveling!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">100pc Self Locking Plastic Bags 2mm Thick All Purpose Storage Baggies</h2>\n  <p>Keep small objects safe and organized with the 100pk 3&quot; x 3&quot; Plastic Bag Set!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>100 All Purpose Baggies</li>\n    <li><strong>Bag Thickness:</strong> 2mm</li>\n    <li><strong>Material:</strong> Clear Plastic</li>\n    <li>Self Locking w/ Single Zipper</li>\n    <li>Reusable/Recloseable</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/home/3x3-zip-bag.jpg\" alt=\"Keep small objects safe and organized with the 100pk 3&quot; x 3&quot; Plastic Bag Set\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 3X4ZB-116</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 685836391708</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Clear</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The 100pk of 3&quot; x 3&quot; Plastic Bags is a great addition to any home, office, garage or workshop. Each set comes with 100 individual clear plastic bags. Each bag is self locking with a single zipper, so they can be used over and over again.</p>\n  <p>These bags are 2mm thick, and measure in at just 3&quot; x 3&quot;, the perfect size for organizing vitamins, medicine, small jewelry and other tiny items while not in use.</p>\n  <p>Make sure to keep a pack of these around for household use, storage and organization while traveling!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "Keep small objects safe and organized with the 100pk 3\" x 3\" Plastic Bag Set! The 100pk of 3\" x 3\" Plastic Bags is a great addition to any home, office, garage or workshop. Each set comes with 100 individual clear plastic bags. Each bag is self locking with a single zipper, so they can be used over and over again. These bags are 2mm thick, and measure in at just 3\" x 3\", the perfect size for organizing vitamins, medicine, small jewelry and other tiny items while not in use. Make sure to keep a pack of these around for household use, storage and organization while traveling!.",
